%h1#icons.section_title Icons
%p To use icons, render the shared icon partial and pass in the name of the icon you want to use.
%p For more information on using SVG icons, please refer to the README for #{link_to('SVÃªGo', 'https://github.com/dabohealth/svego')}.
%pre.preserve_whitespace.line_height_base
  :preserve
    %span.icon.icon_size_base.block
      = render 'shared/icon', icon: '#icon_search'

%h2 Icon Sizes
.row.top_margin_base
